a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t</dd>\n\t\t\t\t</dl>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"sub_foot t_center under_link\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"block\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"f_logo\"><img src=\"//www.vuteq.co.jp/img/common/logo.png\" alt=\"VUTEQ（ビューテック）\" width=\"206\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"//www.vuteq.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>企業サイトはこちら</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"//www.vuteq.co.jp/img/common/ico_blank.gif\" width=\"24\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<small>Copyright&copy; VUTEQ CORPORATION.</small>\n\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</footer>\n\t\t\n\t</div>\n</body>\n<!-- InstanceBeginEditable name=\"body_end\" --><!-- InstanceEndEditable -->\n<!-- InstanceEnd --></html>","finalUrl":"https://www.vuteq.co.jp/recruit/global/strategy/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T21:24:40.629Z"}